Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana a ranar Laraba game da batun shigar da jaridar De Moone Register da aka fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa a cikin China Daily, bayan da ya zargi China da yin watsi da ta da niyyar tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dattijai na Nuwamba 6.
Zargin da Trump ya yi na cewa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka ya nuna sabon matakin da Washington ke yi na kara matsa lamba kan China, kamar yadda jami'an Amurka suka fada wa kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters.
Ko da yake ya zama ruwan dare a yi wa gwamnatocin kasashen waje talla don bunkasa kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington suna cikin yakin kasuwanci mai cike da rikici wanda ya haifar da harajin haraji kan kayayyakin da ake shigowa da su.
An tsara harajin da China ta yi a farkon yakin cinikayya don cutar da masu fitar da kayayyaki da ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump a jihohi kamar Iowa, in ji masana na China da Amurka.
Tsohuwar gwamnan Iowa, Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kasuwanci.
"Sai dai yanzu kasar Sin ta ninka barazanar ta ta hanyar buga tallace-tallace na farfaganda a cikin mujallu masu zaman kansu", in ji Branstad a cikin wani labarin da ya wallafa a cikin jaridar Sundays de Monet Regis.
Don yada farfagandar, gwamnatin China tana amfani da al'adun Amurka na 'yancin magana da wallafe-wallafen kyauta ta hanyar sanya tallace-tallace masu biyan kuɗi a kan De Moyne Register, "in ji Branstad.
"Idan aka kwatanta da wannan, kantunan jaridu da mujallu na titin Beijing, suna da ƙarancin ƙuri'un adawa kuma ba su da ainihin tunani game da ra'ayoyi daban-daban na jama'ar China game da yanayin tattalin arzikin China, la'akari da cewa kafofin watsa labarai suna ƙarƙashin tsananin ikon Jam'iyyar Kwaminis ta Sin", in ji shi.
Ya kara da cewa, "ya ce, daya daga cikin shahararrun jaridun kasar Sin, ya ki amincewa da bukatarsa na buga labarin, ko da yake bai bayyana ko wane ne ba".
Masu sharhi sun ce 'yan Republican na hana mata kada kuri'a kafin rabin wa'adin mulkin saboda gazawar Kavanaugh
Duk da cewa manyan 'yan jam'iyyar Republican sun yi zargin cewa dan takarar babban lauya Brett Kavanaugh ya yi fyade, masu sharhi sun yi gargadin cewa za a fuskanci mummunar martani, musamman daga mata, yayin tsayawa da kare shi a lokacin zaben tsakiyar zango mai zuwa.
"Abubuwan da suka shafi wannan suna da ƙarfi sosai, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican suna nuna sha'awar gaba don turawa ta hanyar jefa kuri'a.
"Ba za mu iya mayar da abubuwan baya ba", in ji Grant Richer, farfesa a fannin kimiyyar siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell ta Jami'ar Syracuse, a wata kasida da aka wallafa a The Hill a ranar Asabar.
Richer ya yi shakkar cewa matsin lamba na minti na karshe na binciken FBI na Sanata Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) zai isa ya sa masu jefa kuri'a su yi fushi.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba - kuma ba za su manta da shi gobe ba", in ji Karin Jean Pierre, mai ba da shawara da kuma kakakin kungiyar masu ci gaba da motsi a watan Nuwamba, a ranar Juma'a, a cewar jaridar Washington, D.C.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a, masu zanga-zangar sun yi zanga-zanga a gaban majalisar dattawa suna ihu cewa, "Laraba tana zuwa!" Kwamitin fassarar dokokin Republican ya zaɓi ya tura takarar Kavanaugh duk da cewa Dr. Kavanaugh ya yi alkawarin bayar da shaida.
"Gurguwar sha'awar dimokiradiyya da kuma motsawa na gab da shuɗewa daga allon rajista", in ji Stu Rosenberg, mai sharhi kan siyasa, wanda ba shi da wani bangare a jam'iyyar siyasa.
Mutane suna cewa ya riga ya tashi, kuma hakan gaskiya ne.
Amma za ta iya tashi musamman tsakanin mata masu jefa kuri'a da matasa masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29, waɗanda ke zaune a cikin ƙauyuka waɗanda ba sa yawan jefa kuri'a, duk da cewa ba sa son shugaban.
Shaidar Ford a gaban jama'a, wanda ke ba da cikakkun bayanai game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i, ya nuna cewa masu sharhi na iya samun mummunan martani daga masu sukar, waɗanda suka tura Jam'iyyun Jamhuriyar Republican don amincewa da shi.
"Wannan ya zama matsala ga GOP", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican na kasa, kamar yadda NBC News ta ruwaito a farkon makon da ya gabata.
"Ba wai kawai game da kuri'ar kwamitin ba, ko kuma kuri'ar karshe, ko kuma yadda Kavanaugh ya zauna a kujerar, amma yadda 'yan Republican suka yi da kuma yadda suka bi da ita", in ji Guy Cecil, darektan kungiyar Priorities USA, wanda ke taimakawa Democrats a zaben, ya nuna wa shafin labarai.
Amma, bayan shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh, jama'ar Amurka sun yi ta rarrabuwa, suna ta karkata zuwa ga abin da ya fi dacewa.
Wani sabon zabe na Yogov ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin dari na masu amsa sun amince da shaidar Ford, ko kuma a'a, kuma kashi 35 cikin dari sun amince da Kavanaugh, ko a'a ko a'a.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun yi imanin cewa Kavanagh ya yi ƙarya a lokacin da yake ba da shaida, kuma kashi 30 cikin ɗari ne kawai suka faɗi haka game da Ford.
Bayan matsin lamba daga Flake, FBI tana binciken tuhumar da aka yi wa Ford da kuma akalla wani daga cikin masu tuhumar, Deborah Ramirez, in ji The Guardian.
A lokacin da Ford ta yi shaida a gaban kwamitin fassara na majalisar dattijai a makon da ya gabata, Kavanaugh ya shaida cewa ta yi mata fyade lokacin da ta ke da shekaru 17 da shan giya.
Babban lauyan Ramirez ya zargi dan takarar da nuna mata al'aurarsa a lokacin bikin da suka yi a lokacin da suke Yale a shekarun 1980.
