Mickelson ya canja matsayinsa a gasar Ryder Cup da aka yi a ranar Asabar
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson ya kafa tarihi a gasar cin kofin Ryder Cup karo na 47 a ranar Lahadi, amma ya canza matsayinsa, ba don nuna wani abu mai ban sha'awa ba.
Mickelson, wanda ke taka leda a gasar cin kofin duniya ta 12 da ake gudanarwa duk shekara biyu, an maye gurbinsa da Jim Furyk a wasan da za a yi a ranar Asabar.
Maimakon zama mai tsananin damuwa kamar yadda ya kasance ga Amurka, mai cin nasara sau biyar ya raba lokacinsa zuwa biyu ta hanyar tallafawa da shirya kansa don wasan don samun sauƙi daga damuwa.
