Kuma idan filin wasa da kansa bai isa ya ba da damar ba, a wasan tara na ranar Lahadi, Mickelson zai yi wasa da Francesco Molinari, wanda ya yi kawance da rookie Tommy Fleetwood a wannan makon don cin nasara duka wasanni huɗu.
Idan ba a fara wasa da kai ba, Mickelson zai iya zama mai mahimmanci a wasan, wanda ya fara wasanni 12 a cikin maki 4 a baya.
Furyk ya bayyana amincewarsa da kansa, ba tare da ya faɗi ƙarin bayani ba.
"Ya fahimci matsayinsa a yanzu, ya buga ni a baya, ya sanya hannunsa a kaina, kuma ya shirya don gobe", in ji Furyk.
"Ya yi imani da kansa sosai.
Yana da ban mamaki, ya kara abubuwa da yawa a cikin rukuni na karshe, kuma wannan makon.
Ban yi tunanin cewa zai ƙara wasanni biyu ba.
Na yi tunani sosai, amma abin da ya faru ke nan, kuma mun yi tunanin cewa ya kamata mu bi wannan hanyar.
Kamar kowa, yana son ya kasance a wurin".
